One person was killed after the car they were travelling in
overturned on Kambula Road in Vryheid, KwaZulu-Natal, on Friday. Kwazulu Private Ambulance Service said when paramedics
arrived at the accident scene, they found that a car had lost control and
overturned, coming to a stop off the road. There were two people in the car, one suffered critical
injuries and was taken to hospital, the second person died at the scene before emergency
services arrived.